title: Fast & Furious 11 (2026) - Vin Diesel, Dwayne Johnson, Jason Statham | Concept Trailer
description:
#FastAndFurious11 #VinDiesel #DwayneJohnson

Watch This Fast & Furious 11 Fan Made Concept Trailer

Vin Diesel's Dom Toretto must ultimately confront his destiny as the Fast & Furious franchise approaches its explosive conclusion, with every main character coming together for one last ride that takes place around the world and pushes the limits of physics the series has already pushed. Dom has taken down international crime syndicates and government conspiracy after ten movies; however, he finds himself facing the only foe that cannot be outrun – his past in the form of foes who have come together specifically to destroy the family that has endured impossible odds through sheer willpower and quarter mile loyalty. Dwayne Johnson will return to the role of Luke Hobbs after years of on-screen tension with Vin Diesel as Hobbs comes to the aid of Dom for the final time since the stakes have grown too large for the family to overcome on its own. Jason Statham's Deckard Shaw completes the three-man team of the most elite warriors that must work together when a new foe emerges with the resources and ferocity of the previous villains were mere speed bumps.

The level of action goes completely overboard with both practical stunts and CGI spectacle combining for a variety of set pieces including cars being dropped from space, highways filled with military vehicles and Dom performing stunts that would be deemed impossible in previous films. There will be true emotional depth as characters that began as street racers and are now globe-trotting heroes face mortality and legacy, asking themselves if their chosen family will survive the final war intact. The competitive energy channeled into mutual respect by Vin Diesel, Dwayne Johnson and Jason Statham due to their experience working together as a team to face danger together shows that sometimes the best teams are formed from individuals who have been adversaries at some point in the past. The reason why this movie is unique is because it understands that everything eventually comes to an end – the film provides massive spectacle while also paying tribute to the individual character arcs developed over twenty years and brings back many faces you may have forgotten existed for moments that truly warrant nostalgia rather than using it for fan service.

Expect cameos from all previous films, returns that serve the story rather than providing a simple cameo fan service and a sendoff that proves family is more than just based on blood – it's the people that you choose to ride with you no matter where the road takes you and no matter how impossible the odds are and how much destruction there is to your name.

Series Premieres in Fall of 2026!
The anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus in Fall 2026!

#dragonball #dragonballsuper

◾️INTRODUCTION
The globally beloved manga DRAGON BALL by Akira Toriyama continues to captivate fans through a wide range of media—from TV animation, movies, games, and merchandising—standing as a top-ranked title with extraordinary worldwide popularity. 
Now, in 2026, the anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus! This ENHANCED edition introduces a large volume of newly added and redrawn cuts, as well as a reconstructed narrative. With cutting-edge visual expression, the series delivers even more immersive battle scenes and a more faithful representation of the original manga—bringing an ENHANCED edition to life like never before.

Several years have passed since the fierce battle against Majin Buu, and Earth has finally regained a brief moment of peace. At the same time, Beerus, the God of Destruction, awakens from his long, deep sleep. Even Kai and Supreme Kai, aware of Beerus’s overwhelming power to destroy entire planets, watch his awakening with great fear… Meanwhile, Beerus hears rumors of a Saiyan who defeated Frieza—and suddenly appears before Goku.
Targeted by Beerus, the strongest being in the universe, Earth is in grave danger. Thus begins an Earth-shattering cosmic battle between the God of Destruction and Goku and his allies—a conflict that will shake the entire universe.
